## Headless VNC Container — Environment Variables
## Copy to .env and adjust values before running docker compose

## VNC password (minimum 6 characters)
VNC_PW=changeme

## Screen resolution (WxH)
VNC_RESOLUTION=1280x1024

## Color depth: 16, 24, or 32
VNC_COL_DEPTH=24

## View-only mode: set to true to prevent keyboard/mouse input via VNC
VNC_VIEW_ONLY=false

## code-server (VS Code in browser) — dev image only
CODE_SERVER_PORT=8443
CODE_SERVER_AUTH=none
## Set to 'password' and add:
## PASSWORD=your-code-server-password

## Traefik reverse proxy integration
TRAEFIK_ENABLE=false
TRAEFIK_HOST=vnc.localhost
TRAEFIK_HOST_DEV=vnc-dev.localhost
